}
```

### Conclusion

In conclusion, while the brute-force method provides a clear and understandable approach, using `JSON.stringify` or leveraging libraries like Lodash can significantly enhance the elegance and readability of your code. Depending on your specific requirements and preferences, you can choose the method that best suits your needs. For simple, small arrays, any of these methods should work effectively.

